# Prisma & Database

- After changing `prisma/schema.prisma`, run `prisma generate` before building or running.
- Use the Prisma client from `@/lib` or where the project initializes it; do not create new client instances in random files.
- Prefer type-safe queries; avoid raw SQL unless necessary.
